metatags.og:title: Munster Parks and Recreation French Lick Resort Casino outing
metatags.og:description: MUNSTER | Tour Highlights: 2-night stay at the lavish French Lick Resort (2 swimming pools and health spa) built to pamper the elite at the turn of the century. Scenic boat cruise on Patoka Lake, Indiana Railway Museum and scenic train ride, Tour of West Baden Springs Naitonal Historic Landmark and Western-style dinner at the Wilstem Guest Ranch. Date: September 24-26. Deposit: $150, with insurance $210. Fees: Single $1,088/Double $799/$Triple $795. Please register by calling (219) 836-7275. For more information, please call (219) 836-PARK.
